IBTrACS (best-track data, storm identities, positions, intensities, RI labels)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
International Best Track Archive for Climate Stewardship (IBTrACS)
Project, Version v04r00 (the version used to build this dataset). NOAA
National Centers for Environmental Information. Dataset DOI (IBTrACS v4,
per NCEI citation guidance): 10.25921/82ty-9e16. Foundational reference:
Knapp, K. R., M. C. Kruk, D. H. Levinson, H. J. Diamond, and
C. J. Neumann, 2010: The International Best Track Archive for Climate
Stewardship (IBTrACS): Unifying tropical cyclone best track data.
